race.comment: ROYAL MOVER (3) hasn't put a hoof wrong stringing two wins together on the bounce to start the career and winning hoop Maloney stays on board following that last-start victory. Drawn to get the run of the race from gate four and is capable of bringing up the hat-trick against this line-up. HA'PENNY HATCH (1) has been right there in all three runs this preparation and looks to be building up to another win. Looms as the main danger. MAKING NEWS (8) broke the maiden status at Eagle Farm last time out and will have derived a stack of confidence from that breakthrough. Include from the inside marble. LITTLE FELLA (7) showed ability saluting at Dalby on debut and has earned his shot at this company. Respect any market confidence. MEET GEORGE (4) strips fitter second-up from the break and may earn some minor money.
